BBNaija 6 star, Nini Singh has shown off all the seven cars she has ever used on Instagram. The automobiles, The Nation gathered, range between N1.8m and N19m with the costliest being 2019 Mercedes Benz GLC 63 AMG 4matic. In a series of InstaStories, Nina noted that her first car was a Nissan Tiida valued at N6million.   Kemi Akindoju: I cry to appreciate art, song or film     King Sunny Ade, NCC DG reward blind singer, Chude Mountain     Eedris Abdulkareem takes a swipe at Charly Boy after 19…   Her second, she revealed, was a 2005 Toyota Corolla sport valued at N1.8million while her third car was a 2008 Ford Edge, valued at N3m, which she said is her utility vehicle. - Advertisement - Nini’s taste grew when she decided to buy her fourth car, a 2014 E-class Sedan sport 4matic valued at N12m. Her love for Mercedes Benz grew and she added two more brands – the 2018 Mercedes Benz GLC 63 AMG 4matic and  2019 Mercedes Benz CLA class – both valued at N19m and N14m respectively.